# CryptoArtGallery

## Overview

CryptoArtGallery showcases the creative potential of blockchain technology through a curated gallery of Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs). This repository aims to promote digital artistry, provide a platform for artists to showcase their work as NFTs, and offer collectors a space to explore and acquire unique digital collectibles.

## Features

- **Curated NFT Collections**: Explore carefully curated collections of digital artworks and virtual assets.
- **Artist Showcases**: Discover featured artists and explore their contributions to the NFT space.
- **Market Insights**: Stay updated with trends and insights into the NFT market.
- **Educational Resources**: Learn about NFT technology, ownership, and blockchain integration.
- **Community Engagement**: Engage in discussions, share insights, and collaborate with fellow NFT enthusiasts.
- **Secure Vault**: Safely store and manage your NFT collections in a secure digital vault.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

Ensure you have the following installed:
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (version 14 or later)
- [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) (version 6 or later)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/CryptoArtGallery.git
   cd CryptoArtGallery
